  "title": "R&D Assistant (Food Industry) #81651",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Food Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>R&D Assistant (Food Industry)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Woodlands (Nearest MRT: Admiralty)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday - Friday: 8.30 AM – 5.30 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support the R&D team with seasoning mixing, new product development, and how products are used.</li><li>Support monthly work on new seasonings or new application methods and help prepare promotional items and presentations.</li><li>Request new raw materials or flavours through the Purchasing team, and manage their registration, documentation, and evaluation.</li><li>Perform QC checks (sensory and visual) on finished products from the seasoning line and on incoming or new raw materials.</li><li>Review and compare current and alternative food ingredients.</li><li>Maintain the R&D lab and keep it clean.</li><li>Carry out plant hygiene checks.</li><li>Support HACCP and Halal systems, including upkeep and documentation.</li><li>Do other tasks assigned by the Company when needed.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Food Science or equivalent.</li><li>Preferably at least 1 year of relevant work experience.</li><li>Candidates without relevant experience are welcome to apply; training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81651 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
